title: What Will Be The Ultimate Goal Of 'Fear the Walking Dead'?
text: Fear the Walking Dead returns tonight after a Labor Day hiatus, back with its third of six episodes in this shortened first season. While the original Walking Dead season one had hordes of zombies and loads of killing and a quite literally an explosive finale, Fear the Walking Dead has been taking things slower so far. Â»
